\c 101 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 101\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Wanta Qajeelaa Jaallachuu, Wanta Hamaamoo Jibbuu (Faarfannaa Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Waa'ee gaarummaa, waa'ee firdii dhugaa nan weeddisa, sagalee mi'aa dhageessisuudhaanis sin faarfadha, yaa Waaqayyo.
\m \bd 2\bd* Ati yoom gara koo dhufta? Waa'ee jireenya balleessaa hin qabnee nan yaada, mana koo keessas garaa balleessaa hin qabneen nan jiraadha;
\m \bd 3\bd* wanta gadhee ija koo dura kaa'ee hin taa'u, irra-daddarbaa nan jibba, akka maxxannee anatti hin qabatu.
\m \bd 4\bd* Yaadni micciiramaan garaa koottii haa fagaatu, waa'ee wanta hamaa beekuu isaa iyyuu hin barbaadu.
\m \bd 5\bd* Dhoksaatti nama kan hamatu, lammaffaa akka hin dubbanne nan godha; nama waan guddaatti of ilaaluuf, nama of bokoksuufis ani obsuu hin danda'u.
\m \bd 6\bd* Iji koo gara warra Waaqayyoof amanamanii biyya keessa taa'anii jira, isaan anaa wajjin haa jiraatan; namni karaa warra balleessaa hin qabnee irra deddeebi'u, anaaf haa hojjetu!
\m \bd 7\bd* Namni haxxummaadhaan hojjetu, mana koo keessa hin jiraatu, namni soba dubbatu ija koo dura hin dhaabatu.
\m \bd 8\bd* Namoota hamaa hojjetan hundumaa mandara Waaqayyoo keessaa balleessuudhaaf, ganama ganama jal'oota biyya keessa jiran hundumaa lammaffaa akka hin dubbanne nan godha.
\b 
